{
  "name": "SW: Send Email via Resend",
  "description": "Subworkflow: send one transactional email via Resend (to, subject, html, optional attachments). From address from CONFIG; logs to Automations Log and alerts on failure. Used across outreach, sales, onboarding, and client success.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## SW: Send Email via Resend\n\n**Subworkflow.** Sends a single transactional email via the Resend API. From address comes from CONFIG; used for outreach, onboarding, invoices, weekly updates, and referrals.\n\n**Input (full payload):** `to` (required), `subject` (required), `html` (required), `attachments` (optional, array of `{ filename, content }` base64), `workflowName` (optional, for logging). **n8n 2.x:** In the parent workflow, the Execute Sub-workflow node must map these fields under **Workflow Inputs** (passing only the previous node is not enough when using workflow ID).\n\n**Output:** `{ success, data: { sent, emailId, to }, error }`. Logs to Automations Log and alerts on failure.",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "9082e780-217a-490f-a66c-d80d9fdaf800",
      "name": "Note — About this workflow",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [
        176,
        -96
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "inputSource": "passthrough"
      },
      "id": "c9dbe382-aecb-4dca-a8e3-d30cdd86771d",
      "name": "Execute Workflow Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.executeWorkflowTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [
        176,
        224
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const input = $('Execute Workflow Trigger').first().json;\nconst config = $('Call \\'CONFIG — Global Settings\\'').first().json;\n\nif (!input.to) {\n  const keys = input && typeof input === 'object' ? Object.keys(input).join(', ') : String(input);\n  throw new Error('Missing required field \"to\". Map Workflow Inputs in the Execute Sub-workflow node: to, subject, html (and optional workflowName). Expected { to, subject, html }. Received keys: ' + keys);\n}\nif (!input.subject) {\n  throw new Error('Missing required field \"subject\". The calling workflow must pass { to, subject, html }.');\n}\nif (!input.html) {\n  throw new Error('Missing required field \"html\". The calling workflow must pass { to, subject, html }.');\n}\n\nconst from = `${config.owner.fromName} <${config.owner.fromEmail}>`;\n\nconst payload = {\n  from: from,\n  to: [input.to],\n  subject: input.subject,\n  html: input.html\n};\n\nif (input.attachments) {\n  payload.attachments = input.attachments;\n}\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    payload: payload,\n    workflowName: input.workflowName || 'SW: Send Email via Resend',\n    to: input.to\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "15a1d2ab-3522-4836-9edc-ba822d26f4d3",
      "name": "Prepare Email",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        624,
        224
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.resend.com/emails",
        "authentication": "predefinedCredentialType",
        "nodeCredentialType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
